caption: Great lunch option, you can sit down and be done within 30min if there isn't a wait. Filling, great quality fish accompanied by deliscious sushi rice at a reasonable price! Highly recommend.
Never been hear but wow what a good name for the area hope y’all are successful

I've ordered the tenders with the fries, Although the seasoning is alright, the quality of the chicken is worse then fast-food ground meat. It looks to be a frozen ground meat patties being sold by corporate companies.. the fries were soggy. Bad experience overall.

Wow, really delicious! I have always loved Philly's Best (from Buffalo myself) saw the pop-up and wondered why and now I know... amazing chicken. Best I've had in Chicago. Sorry I waited so long to get it. Hope it will be around for awhile!

This sandwich might have been good but I wouldn’t really know bc it was delivered to me missing half the ingredients. All it came with was chicken and pickles, it was supposed to have coleslaw, cheese and some kind of creamy sauce none of which was on it. The fries were incredibly soggy and not at all seasoned. The ranch I paid 1.50 for was also super low quality. I really don’t understand how you just totally neglect to add more than half the toppings to a sandwich?!  EDIT TO REVIEW:  They offered to bring me a new sandwich another day on the house. Great service and the sandwich with everything on it was excellent. Also tried the macaroni this time which I’d highly recommend also.

***MUST TRY***  This was my first time hearing of and enjoying food from this restaurant.  1.) The flavor. Unbelievable. I had the tenders made zesty and had to try their comeback sauce. Reminded me of my visit to Nashville. The bread at the bottom absorbed ALLLL of that spicy grease, and was still butter grilled or toasted (not sure which). It was the cherry on top. 👍🏼👍🏼👍🏼 2.) The customer service, even after 1am. 👍🏼👍🏼👍🏼I chose to have my order delivered by a 3rd party delivery service(my fault), and they failed me at every step. Not only was the employee who took my call regarding my orders status very kind and genuine, he offered to help me by contacting the 3rd party delivery to fix it how he could. Bravo!  Thoroughly impressed and will be eating from here again. Definitely dining in though.
